---

<div class="glass-card p-3 sm:p-5 mt-6 sm:mt-8">
  <h2 class="text-heading mb-3 sm:mb-5 text-center text-sm sm:text-xl">ðŸ“Š Detailed Raid Results (Last 5 Raids)</h2>
